	<clause id="_atomic_subatomic_and_molecular_units" obligation="normative"><title>Atomic, subatomic and molecular units</title><note id="_6d385535-a697-4c48-a58b-5ffcf93a6b7e">
	<p id="_e0d445e0-98d3-4731-b081-7e10f22c06e9">This section focuses on atomic physics rather than chemistry.</p>
